com.opengamma.strata.pricer.calculator

Class CashflowEquivalentTheoreticalCalculator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.opengamma.strata.pricer.calculator.CashflowEquivalentTheoreticalCalculator

  • public class CashflowEquivalentTheoreticalCalculator
extends Object
    Calculator to compute the cash flow equivalent of some interest rate derivative. The "equivalence" is based on a single curve simplifying assumption.

    The calculator also provides methods to compute present value and present value sensitivity of the objects describing the cash-flows.
